== 發行 ==
[[華納兄弟|華納兄弟]]最初將電影排定於2016年3月11日在美國上映<ref>{{cite news|last1=A. Lincoln|first1=Ross|title=‘The Accountant’, ‘Project XX’, And More Get Release Dates|url=http://deadline.com/2015/05/warner-bros-release-dates-the-accountant-project-xx-1201430106/|accessdate=2015-05-23|work=deadline.com|date=2015-05-19|archive-date=2021-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210211215125/https://deadline.com/2015/05/warner-bros-release-dates-the-accountant-project-xx-1201430106/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，後於2015年11月，上映日延遲至2016年8月19日<ref>{{cite web |author=Anthony D'Alessandro |url=http://deadline.com/2015/11/arms-the-dudes-the-house-project-xx-release-dates-warner-bros-1201620910/ |title=Warner Bros. Moves Todd Phillips’ ‘Arms & The Dudes’ To Summer |publisher=Deadline |date= |accessdate=2015-11-14 |archive-date=2021-02-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210211172526/https://deadline.com/2015/11/arms-the-dudes-the-house-project-xx-release-dates-warner-bros-1201620910/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 評價 ===
[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]新鮮度60%，基於179條評論，平均分為6/10<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/war_dogs_2016/ |title=War Dogs (2016) |publisher=Rotten Tomatoes |accessdate=2016-08-17 |archive-date=2019-05-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190510201523/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/war_dogs_2016/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]得分57<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/war-dogs|title=War Dogs reviews|publisher=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]|accessdate=2016-08-17|archive-date=2021-01-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210123135601/https://www.metacritic.com/movie/war-dogs|dead-url=no}}</ref>，評價兩極但正面偏多。

=== 票房 ===
在美國，電影於2016年8月19日上映，與《[[賓漢_(2016年電影)|賓漢]]》、《[[酷寶：魔弦傳說|酷寶：魔弦傳說]]》，並預計於首映週末從3100間戲院中得到1200萬至1500萬美元的票房<ref name="preview">{{cite web|url=http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/envelope/cotown/la-et-ct-movie-projector-20160815-snap-story.html|title='Ben-Hur' remake likely won't be able to topple 'Suicide Squad' at the box office|publisher=Los Angeles Times|accessdate=2016-08-18|archive-date=2017-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170924183540/http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/envelope/cotown/la-et-ct-movie-projector-20160815-snap-story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在美國首映週末，電影獲得1430萬美元的票房，名列第三並成為新片中的冠軍<ref name="opening">{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2016/08/ben-hur-war-dogs-suicide-squad-sausage-party-weekend-box-office-1201805947/|title=‘Suicide Squad’ Holding No. 1 Turf; ‘War Dogs’ & ‘Kubo’ In Staring Contest; ‘Ben-Hur’ Crashing|publisher=deadline.com|accessdate=2016-08-22|archive-date=2017-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170924224950/http://deadline.com/2016/08/ben-hur-war-dogs-suicide-squad-sausage-party-weekend-box-office-1201805947/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

